# Images Directory

This directory stores static images for the Flask application.

## Usage

**Local Development:**
- Reference in templates: `/static/images/filename.png`
- Served at: `http://localhost:5001/static/images/filename.png`

**Production (Railway.app):**
- Served at: `https://your-app.railway.app/static/images/filename.png`
- Use these URLs in email templates instead of base64 encoding

## Recommended Images

- `logo.png` - Business logo for emails and web UI
- `header-banner.png` - Email template header
- `favicon.ico` - Website favicon
